                <ul class="guide-tabs__item-list">
                  <li>
                    <div class="guide-tabs__company-item-list-inner">
                      <span class="guide-tabs__item-number">昭和51年</span>
                      <span class="guide-tabs__item-text"
                        >民宿桑留居荘 設立</span
